##     带in条件的查询
explain select /*+use_px parallel(3) full()*/ * from t1 where a in (1,2,3,4,5) order by a,b,c,d;;
Query Plan
=====================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                    |NAME|EST. ROWS|COST|
-----------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN MERGE SORT DISTR|    |5        |182 |
|1 | EXCHANGE OUT DISTR         |    |5        |180 |
|2 |  GRANULE ITERATOR          |    |5        |180 |
|3 |   TABLE SCAN               |t1  |5        |180 |
=====================================================

Outputs & filters: 
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([t1.a], [t1.b], [t1.c], [t1.d], [t1.e]), filter(nil), sort_keys([t1.a, ASC], [t1.b, ASC], [t1.c, ASC], [t1.d, ASC])
  1 - output([t1.a], [t1.b], [t1.c], [t1.d], [t1.e]), filter(nil)
  2 - output([t1.a], [t1.b], [t1.c], [t1.d], [t1.e]), filter(nil)
  3 - output([t1.a], [t1.b], [t1.c], [t1.d], [t1.e]), filter(nil), 
      access([t1.a], [t1.b], [t1.c], [t1.d], [t1.e]), partitions(p0)

select /*+use_px parallel(3) full()*/ * from t1 where a in (1,2,3,4,5) order by a,b,c,d;;
